    "question": {
      "en": "2026 Update: When a 'Move Over' law is in effect, what must you do?",
      "zh-Hans": "2026年更新：当“避让法（Move Over）”生效时，您必须做什么？",
      "zh-Hant": "2026年更新：當「避讓法（Move Over）」生效時，您必須做什麼？"
    },
    "options": {
      "A": { "en": "Change lanes away from emergency vehicles or slow down significantly.", "zh-Hans": "变换车道避开路边的紧急车辆，或者显著减速。", "zh-Hant": "變換車道避開路邊的緊急車輛，或者顯著減速。" },
      "B": { "en": "Stop in your lane.", "zh-Hans": "在原车道停车。", "zh-Hant": "在原車道停車。" },
      "C": { "en": "Speed up to pass them faster.", "zh-Hans": "加速以便更快通过。", "zh-Hant": "加速以便更快通過。" }
    },
    "answer": "A",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "The Move Over law protects emergency workers, tow trucks, and Caltrans vehicles on the roadside.",
      "zh-Hans": "如果路边有闪灯的救护车、警车或拖车，您必须在安全的情况下换到左边车道，否则必须大幅减速。",
