  {
    "id": 108,
    "category": "Literacy",
    "question": {
      "en": "At an intersection, which direction should you scan first?",
      "zh-Hans": "在十字路口，您应该先观察哪个方向？",
      "zh-Hant": "在十字路口，您應該先觀察哪個方向？"
    },
    "options": {
      "A": { "en": "Right.", "zh-Hans": "右侧。", "zh-Hant": "右側。" },
      "B": { "en": "Left.", "zh-Hans": "左侧。", "zh-Hant": "左側。" },
      "C": { "en": "Behind you.", "zh-Hans": "后方。", "zh-Hant": "後方。" }
    },
    "answer": "B",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Cars coming from the left are closer to you and pose an immediate danger.",
      "zh-Hans": "左侧的车辆会最先穿过您的行驶路径，因此应先看左，再看右，然后再看一次左。",
