  },
  {
    "id": 121,
    "category": "Literacy",
    "question": {
      "en": "When a 'Merge' sign is posted on the freeway, you should:",
      "zh-Hans": "当高速公路上有“汇入（Merge）”标志时，您应该：",
      "zh-Hant": "當高速公路上有「匯入（Merge）」標誌時，您應該："
    },
    "options": {
      "A": { "en": "Stop and wait for a gap.", "zh-Hans": "停车等待空隙。", "zh-Hant": "停車等待空隙。" },
      "B": { "en": "Slow down or speed up to match the flow of traffic.", "zh-Hans": "减速或加速以配合车流速度。", "zh-Hant": "減速或加速以配合車流速度。" },
      "C": { "en": "Always yield, as merging traffic has no rights.", "zh-Hans": "始终让行，因为汇入车辆没有优先权。", "zh-Hant": "始終讓行，因為匯入車輛沒有優先權。" }
    },
    "answer": "B",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Merging requires matching the speed of the existing traffic to enter the flow safely.",
      "zh-Hans": "汇入的精髓在于速度匹配。停车会非常危险，应调整速度寻找安全切入点。",
      "zh-Hant": "匯入的精髓在於速度匹配。停車會非常危險，應調整速度尋找安全切入點。"
    },
    "dmv_ref": { "page": "44", "section": "Section 7: Entering/Exiting" }
  },
  {
